      &lt;updatePomFile&gt;true&lt;/updatePomFile&gt;
      &lt;flattenMode&gt;resolveCiFriendliesOnly&lt;/flattenMode&gt;
    &lt;/configuration&gt;  

I believe you have to add this configuration for ci-friendly projects, as explained [here](https://maven.apache.org/maven-ci-friendly.html#install-deploy).

